JOHSNNESBURG - South Africa has only produced one grand slam winner in Gary Player. Golf’s holy grail is not easily attainable - only five players in the history of the sport have managed to win all four majors. But if Jayden Schaper’s exploits on the golf course last year are anything to go by, he might have a shot at joining the Black Knight on that illustrious list. eNCA reporter OG Molefe, got to spend the day with the teenager. *Watch the full story in the gallery above eNCA